review_blob: Natti Light is the greatest thing that has ever happened to me!  The soft, metallic taste left in your mouth after a good shotgun of the all natural beer leaves one with a grin.  For 10 bucks a thirty pack there is no competition for this 12 oz. peice of heaven.  A perfect choice for case races, beer pong, kings, beer ball, bonging, shotgunning, or just plain chugging.
